     F** MBDR32 *********************************************************
     F*  PROGRAM    : CREATE CSV FILE FOR PAST N MONTH NO RESULT LIST   *
     F*             : (STEP2)                                           *
     F*  WRITTEN    : 02/12/2016                                        *
     F*  WRITTEN BY : JW (SRA)                                          *
     F*  FUNCTION   : READ MBDWP31 AND PRINT REPORT                     *
     F*
JW1  F*  J.WATANABE 05/10/2016 MODIFY PAST MONTH ACCEPT 0 (MONTH)       *
JW2  F*  J.WATANABE 12/14/2016 ADD 15 LOCATION                          *
JW3  F*  J.WATANABE 04/12/2017 ADD PARAMERT (USER)                      *
JW4  F*  J.WATANABE 05/15/2018 FIX BUG                                  *
     F*******************************************************************
     FMBDWP31 IF  E                    DISK
     FFGBPL01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FFCEPL01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FFCEPL30 IF  E           K        DISK
     FMBDWP32 UF  E           K        DISK                      A
     FMBDPL14 IF  E           K        DISK
JW2  FAAMPL11 IF  E           K        DISK
     E                    NON        10  4
     E                    NAM        10 15
     E                    TLS1    1   1 60
JW2  E                    KNB        15  6
JW2  E                    KQT        15  6
JW2  E                    KHZ        15 10 0
JW2  E                    M2L        15 10
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80@TODAY
     I                                        1   40@TDYYY
     I                                        5   60@TDYMM
     I                                        7   80@TDYDD
     I            DS
     I                                        1  60 @HEAD
     I                                        1   9 @HEAD1
     I                                       10  43 @HEAD2
     I                                       44  51 @HEAD3
     I                                       52  60 @HEAD4
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80A2TAHZ
     I                                        1   40A2TAYY
     I                                        5   60A2TAMM
     I                                        7   80A2TADD
     I            DS
     I                                        1  12 M1SHIN
     I                                        1  10 MSHN10
     I                                        1   5 M1SHN1
     I                                        6  10 M1SHN2
     I                                       11  12 M1SHN3
     I            DS
     I                                        1  15 M1MHIN
     I                                        1  10 MMHN10
     I                                        1   5 MMHN1
     I                                        6  10 MMHN2
     I                                       11  15 MMHN3
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80M1TAHZ
     I                                        1   60MTAYM
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80B2SKHZ
     I                                        1   40B2SKYY
     I                                        5   60B2SKMM
     I                                        7   80B2SKDD
     I            DS
     I                                        1  14 XSHN
     I                                        1   5 MXSHN1
     I                                        6   6 H1A
     I                                        7  11 MXSHN2
     I                                       12  12 H1B
     I                                       13  14 MXSHN3
     I            DS
     I                                        1   9 SLOC
     I                                        1   1 F3STRK
     I                                        2   2 H3A
     I                                        3   4 F3STRT
     I                                        5   5 H3B
     I                                        6   7 F3STRR
     I                                        8   8 H3C
     I                                        9   9 F3STRD
     I            DS
     I                                        1  40 M2NON
     I                                        1   4 M2NON1
     I                                        5   8 M2NON2
     I                                        9  12 M2NON3
     I                                       13  16 M2NON4
     I                                       17  20 M2NON5
     I                                       21  24 M2NON6
     I                                       25  28 M2NON7
     I                                       29  32 M2NON8
     I                                       33  36 M2NON9
     I                                       37  40 M2NONA
     I            DS
     I                                        1 150 M2NAM
     I                                        1  15 M2NAM1
     I                                       16  30 M2NAM2
     I                                       31  45 M2NAM3
     I                                       46  60 M2NAM4
     I                                       61  75 M2NAM5
     I                                       76  90 M2NAM6
     I                                       91 105 M2NAM7
     I                                      106 120 M2NAM8
     I                                      121 135 M2NAM9
     I                                      136 150 M2NAMA
JW2   * CHANGE DATE (KHZ)
 |   I            DS
 |   I                                        1 150 KHZ
 |   I                                        1  100CKHZ01
 |   I                                       11  200CKHZ02
 |   I                                       21  300CKHZ03
